# Dessmonitor Project Overview

**Monorepo**: `app` (React + Vite) + `server` (NestJS)

**Stack**:
- app: React 19, Vite 7, TypeScript 5.9, Tailwind CSS v4
- server: NestJS

**Structure**:
- `app/` — frontend (index.html, vite.config.ts, src/)
- `server/` — NestJS backend (src/main.ts)

**Server API**:
- `GET /credentials/status` — check if credentials are configured
- `GET /data/latest` — latest device data (pars, gts, fetchedAt)
- `GET /data/chart?field=&start=&end=` — chart data for a field
- `GET /data/key-param?parameter=&start=&end=` — key parameter time series

**Commands**:
- `npm run dev` / `npm run dev:app` — start frontend dev server
- `npm run dev:server` — start NestJS in watch mode
- `npm run build` / `npm run build:app` — build frontend
- `npm run build:server` — build server
- `npm run lint` — lint all workspaces

**Conventions**:
- **File names**: use kebab-case (e.g. `battery-status.tsx`, `use-battery.ts`)
- Use functional components and hooks
- Prefer named exports for utilities; default export for page/route components
- Use Tailwind utility classes for styling (no inline styles unless necessary)
- Strict TypeScript — enable `noUnusedLocals`, `noUnusedParameters`
